channel.title: ~~~"+playername+ is Already Online"~~~ WTF, No They Arnt! ~~~
channel.description:
On my server, evey 10-20 minutes, it kicked everybody off, and in the batch logs, it says: " *playername* is already online" So, I have to crash and reboot the server. Anyone know what this is? And no, its not that the max ammount of players was reached.
Thx
